  "texts": [
    "This occurred in two situations.",
    "One was that certain abnormalities were annotated by one expert but not by another expert, and the other was that certain abnormalities were annotated differently by two experts.",
    "We further counted the number of bounding boxes with IoU=0 for each abnormality and found that the maximal number was 14 in the interreader study (<0.023 per CXR) and the maximal number was 6 in the intrareader study (<0.01 per CXR).",
    "Detailed information can be found in Supplementary Table 3.",
    "These results demonstrated the good interreader and intrareader agreement of annotations."
  ],
